{
  "title": "Circle",
  "description": "Mutable circle shape defined by a centre position and radius. Implements ShapeLike for use in the collision pipeline. For SAT-based collision the circle is approximated as a regular polygon with Circle.collisionSegments sides; normals and vertices are cached and regenerated lazily when the shape mutates. `Circle.temp` is a shared scratch instance for intermediate calculations.",
